[1.] 
Sending mail-attachment > 45k with Netscape via sendmail hangs
[2.]
I am experiencing a problem when sending mail from
Netscape v4.5 (using outgoing mail server==localhost)
Whenever I include an attachment bigger that ~45k, netscape
hangs trying to send the message (or waiting for sendmail
to do the job...). In fact, two sendmail processes are left
in background when that happens.
I do not experience the same behavior with kernel 2.0.36.
[3.]
networking, sendmail, netscape
